<br />
<br />

## Pipeline

- Load Dataset

`gtf.Dataset(root_dir, img_dir, anno_file, batch_size=batch_size);`

- Load Model

`gtf.Model(model_name, use_pretrained=pretrained, use_gpu=gpu);`

- Set Hyper-parameter

`gtf.Set_Learning_Rate(0.001);`

- Train

`gtf.Train(epochs, params_file);`



